{"id": 1604, "genre": 1000, "title": "新一波互联网名词，你厌烦哪些？", "description": "\"创业就创业吧，整这些故弄玄虚玩意儿干啥！”系列之二。欢迎在评论区补充。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 12535, "comment_count": 57, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170401180647W9ptcgEwJNLTOoYm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-04T17:00:33Z", "questions": [{"id": 2115, "title": "新一波互联网名词，你厌烦哪些？", "content": "新一波互联网名词，你厌烦哪些？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 186342, "content": "“VR突破口”，表达的都是“我为啥还找不着VR赚钱路子”的焦虑", "image": "img/option/option/20170401181043g92LwMzJujFTs0Vq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186343, "content": "“阅读降维”，严肃新闻标题党化和今日头条化", "image": "img/option/option/20170401181240chzPnYCU4JyFwtDl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186344, "content": "“互联网下半场”，上半场烧钱打死对手，下半场半死不活等收购", "image": "img/option/option/20170401181408ijrQ9Kd1Tcs76uba.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186346, "content": "“知识付费”，原来那些免费都懒得看的信息现在只要十元，统统十元！", "image": "img/option/option/20170401181708a9szrIELUm6cWiGx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186347, "content": "“人格跃迁”，满足用户成为更好（更会花钱）的自己的期待", "image": "img/option/option/20170401182023vOwipr57jAVgBNyT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186348, "content": "“AI挑战一切”，各种跟风Alpha Go，除了棋牌你们能搞点实用的？", "image": "img/option/option/20170401182138ZONP128oeIWrRJgh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186349, "content": "“新物种”，黑科技不够吹的，都开始发明新物种了", "image": "img/option/option/201704011823164YrnjgyU6pLAEPO8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 186351, "content": "“互联网+新法则：降维攻击”，大刘表示：你们说的是个啥？", "image": "img/option/option/20170401182359tx0lahSyDJL4QZIG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}